def process_test_case(n, a, b):
    a.sort()  # Sp xp i A
    b.sort()  # Sp xp i B
    
    # So snh tng thnh vin ca i A v B
    for i in range(n):
        if a[i] > b[i]:  # Nu thnh vin i A mnh hn thnh vin i B
            return "NO"
    return "YES"

    a = list(map(int, input().split()))  # Sc mnh i A
    b = list(map(int, input().split()))  # Sc mnh i B
    
    # Gi hm x l v in kt qu
    print(process_test_case(n, a, b))

# Hm x l mt test case
def process_test_case(n, a, b):
    a.sort()  # Sp xp i A
    b.sort()  # Sp xp i B
    
    # So snh tng thnh vin ca i A v B
    for i in range(n):
        if a[i] > b[i]:  # Nu thnh vin i A mnh hn thnh vin i B
            return "NO"
    return "YES"

    a = list(map(int, input().split()))  # Sc mnh i A
    b = list(map(int, input().split()))  # Sc mnh i B
    
    # Gi hm x l v in kt qu
    print(process_test_case(n, a, b))
